<Author>jaymanek
<Content>Great Hotel Not Luxury Though Well I booked this hotel as a final stop on our honeymoon.. I have just checked out and am writing this as i wait for my taxi...We spent four days here after touring brazil  argentina. We stayed at 5* hotels all the way. I didnt book a 5* in miami as i knew we would be out most of the time and didnt want to waste cash for no reason.When i booked in jan08 most of the reviews were positive on this site. When i logged on from brazil the night before arrival, i was shaking in my boots... was very nervous at what we might find... This is our honeymoon after all!So when we arived at 4am, no one was around, the place was a ghost town.. but what did i expect... Finally got checked in..I went around the room carefully after reading some of the comments on here.There was one little hair in the bathroom but thats all. The place was very clean.The bed is fun for jumping around on but not so good for my back which is hurting a little after 4 nightsThe hotel has fantastic facilities. The breakfast is the best we had on our entire trip, but that maynot be saying much as the 5* hotels in south america tend to stick to continental..We ate a lot at the $19.95 buffet and then were good for the whole day.The pool area is excellent with the beach right there. Water is clear and blue! The pool area has good entertainment at weekends.Like i said we were out a lot, but the hotel had a lot to offer for those who just want to stay by the pool all day.The hotel is huge and is very very busy... people around all the time and guests that we talked to were very happy with the place.Staff are very courteous and helpful.Its a little further than we thought from south beach.. but we are english and the pound is strong so didnt mind the $12 cab fares to ocean drive or lincoln rd...Overall hotel is NOT luxury as it makes out... But is a nice hotel with good sized rooms and good ameneities.We would stay here again if we had kids or just wanted to relax on the gorgeous beach... But if just us two were coming again we would probably be going to the loews or one of the other top hotels.Dont discount it based on the other reviews though as its a good place and we enjoyed it here..Thanks and hope this helps.. 
